title: 2 bed 1 ba 8 Month Winter Rental Furnished w all utilities
posting_body: ['Available September 1, 2022 through April 30, 2023.', ' Charming Executive 2 bed 1 ba  Move-in ready, fully Furnished Victorian with a huge backyard and mature gardens to enjoy on a quiet, peaceful, safe, dead end street.', ' Walk to downtown Andover in 8 minutes, close to train, Whole Foods, Post Office, gas stations, drug store, Main Street shopping, dining and entertainment.', ' Kitchen/Dining room is furnished with dining table and 4 sturdy chairs, all appliances, pots, pans, bakeware, silverware, dishes, glasses, bowls, French press, mugs, microwave, kitchen towels, cleaning products, ceiling lights with fan.', ' Bathroom has tub and shower with curtain, standard sink, toilet, 4 storage cabinets, large body towels, hand towels, facecloths.', ' Living room is furnished with sofa, Smart TV, Sony Sound bar with sub-woofer,  coffee table with matching side tables, 2 matching lamps.', 'Primary Bedroom is furnished with a queen size bed, new sheet set, new pillows, comforter, 2 end tables with lamps, a full size dresser and mirror, 2 walk in closets.', '2nd bedroom can be used as an office which includes a Multifunction printer/scanner/copier.', ' Spare toner, spare drum and 3 reams of letter size paper on a stand up desk.', ' Large private front porch with furniture.', ' Large private side deck.', ' Sunroom with furniture.', ' 2 dedicated parking spots next to house.', ' All utilities, heat, electric, cooking fuel, gas, water, basic cable, basic internet, trash pickup and yard maintenance included.', 'Upgrades available for cable & internet.']
